Sheet 1 – Customers

| Column Name     | Data Type | Description                |
| --------------- | --------- | -------------------------- |
| customer_id     | INTEGER   | Unique customer identifier |
| customer_code   | VARCHAR   | Customer code              |
| first_name      | VARCHAR   | Customer first name        |
| last_name       | VARCHAR   | Customer last name         |
| gender          | VARCHAR   | Gender                     |
| date_of_birth   | DATE      | Customer DOB               |
| email           | VARCHAR   | Email address              |
| phone           | VARCHAR   | Mobile number              |
| city            | VARCHAR   | Customer city              |
| state           | VARCHAR   | Customer state             |
| annual_income   | DECIMAL   | Annual income              |
| credit_score    | INTEGER   | Credit score               |
| join_date       | DATE      | Customer joining date      |
| customer_status | VARCHAR   | Active / Inactive          |

Sheet 2 – Accounts

| Column Name           | Data Type | Description           |
| --------------------- | --------- | --------------------- |
| account_id            | INTEGER   | Unique account ID     |
| account_number        | VARCHAR   | Bank account number   |
| customer_id           | INTEGER   | Customer ID           |
| branch_id             | INTEGER   | Branch ID             |
| account_type_id       | INTEGER   | Account type          |
| balance               | DECIMAL   | Current balance       |
| open_date             | DATE      | Account opening date  |
| account_status        | VARCHAR   | Active / Closed       |
| last_transaction_date | DATE      | Last transaction date |

Sheet 3 – Transactions

| Column Name      | Data Type | Description                        |
| ---------------- | --------- | ---------------------------------- |
| transaction_id   | INTEGER   | Transaction ID                     |
| account_id       | INTEGER   | Account ID                         |
| merchant_id      | INTEGER   | Merchant ID                        |
| transaction_date | TIMESTAMP | Transaction date                   |
| transaction_type | VARCHAR   | Deposit, Withdrawal, Transfer etc. |
| amount           | DECIMAL   | Transaction amount                 |
| status           | VARCHAR   | Success, Failed, Pending           |
| channel          | VARCHAR   | UPI, ATM, POS, NEFT, IMPS          |
| device_type      | VARCHAR   | Mobile, ATM, Desktop etc.          |
| is_international | BOOLEAN   | International transaction flag     |
| transaction_city | VARCHAR   | Transaction city                   |
| currency         | VARCHAR   | Transaction currency               |


Sheet 4 – Loans

| Column Name         | Data Type | Description                 |
| ------------------- | --------- | --------------------------- |
| loan_id             | INTEGER   | Loan ID                     |
| customer_id         | INTEGER   | Customer ID                 |
| loan_type_id        | INTEGER   | Loan type                   |
| loan_amount         | DECIMAL   | Loan amount                 |
| interest_rate       | DECIMAL   | Interest rate               |
| tenure_months       | INTEGER   | Loan tenure                 |
| emi_amount          | DECIMAL   | EMI                         |
| loan_start_date     | DATE      | Loan start                  |
| loan_end_date       | DATE      | Loan end                    |
| default_flag        | BOOLEAN   | Loan default flag           |
| loan_status         | VARCHAR   | Active / Closed / Defaulted |
| remaining_balance   | DECIMAL   | Remaining balance           |
| outstanding_balance | DECIMAL   | Outstanding amount          |
| last_payment_date   | DATE      | Last payment                |


Sheet 5 – Branches

| Column Name    | Data Type | Description    |
| -------------- | --------- | -------------- |
| branch_id      | INTEGER   | Branch ID      |
| branch_code    | VARCHAR   | Branch code    |
| branch_name    | VARCHAR   | Branch name    |
| city           | VARCHAR   | Branch city    |
| state          | VARCHAR   | Branch state   |
| manager_name   | VARCHAR   | Branch manager |
| employee_count | INTEGER   | Employees      |
| opening_date   | DATE      | Opening date   |
| region         | VARCHAR   | Bank region    |

Sheet 6 – Merchants

| Column Name       | Data Type | Description       |
| ----------------- | --------- | ----------------- |
| merchant_id       | INTEGER   | Merchant ID       |
| merchant_name     | VARCHAR   | Merchant name     |
| merchant_category | VARCHAR   | Merchant category |
| city              | VARCHAR   | Merchant city     |
| state             | VARCHAR   | Merchant state    |

Sheet 7 – Master Tables

| Column            | Description                             |
| ----------------- | --------------------------------------- |
| account_type_id   | Account Type ID                         |
| account_type_name | Savings, Current, Salary, Fixed Deposit |


Loan Types

